* Notes
** Biblical call to justice
*** How to behave around police officers
Black kids were taught what to do if a police officer was near them, such as how to act, where to put their hands, and how to make themselves look as unthreatening as possible. White kids were taught nothing of that sort.
*** Catholic social teaching is liberating
But others believe it is threatening
** Texas detention facility
*** Stats
+ 250 infants, children, and teenagers being held
+ Inadequate food, water, and sanition
+ 300 children per cell
+ No adult supervision, children unable to support other children
